            <lg xml:id="TK957">
<l>kuṭippiṟantār kaṇviḷaṅkuṅ kuṟṟam vicumpiṉ</l>
<l>matikkaṇ maṟuppō luyarntu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The defects of the noble will be observed as clearly as the dark spots in the moon.</l>
